These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-6-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, june
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, swimming
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, writing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, ambient
1. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
2. the fan ambient is not the person who's sport is swimming##6
3. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |      2      |
| Beverage   | june      | march    |
| Food       | swimming       | skiing    |
| Hobby      | writing     | board-games |
| Job        | jazz | ambient     |

