.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-6-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, iris
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, time-travel
2 different pets are kept: rat, goldfish
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, strawberry
1. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who growslily##1
3. the person eating nectarine is not the person who growsiris##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | iris | lily         |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | time-travel |
| Sport         | rat      | goldfish  |
| Transport     | strawberry        | nectarine    |

