The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, pilot
1. the person eating raspberry is on the far left##1
2. the blend-smoker is not the person drinking 7up##6
3. the journalist is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | 7up        |
| Hobby         | blend | aristoff |
| Movie-Genre   | raspberry      | peas |
| Transport     | journalist    | pilot |

