1. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
2. the person playing go is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Hobby         | gardening  | singing |
| Job           | blood-red | white  |
| Movie-Genre   | backgammon | go |
| Pet           | hot-chocolate     | lemonade     |

